<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/basic-income-and-the-anti-slavery-movement/">Basic Income and the Anti-Slavery Movement</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Unconditional basic income is not only feasible, but it also has more emancipatory potential than any other single policy.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
